{"tid":1679954,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【硬件科普】B365主板相对于B360主板是缩水？大错特错，详解B365与B360芯片组的区别","createTime":"2019-10-28T13:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T06:42:34.000Z","uid":61763,"like":0,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1427d36745c425f05caf67a11992230ef07d8c","tid":1679954,"uid":61763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:29:59.000Z","msg":"大陆仔就是硬核, 连登仔吃屎吧, 装逼仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av73494011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav73494011&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD51e0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=4bb6974f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av73494011</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/_aZGLeYI2jsdAmEK9zH82w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2F_aZGLeYI2jsdAmEK9zH82w&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD51e0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=c55c05ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/_aZGLeYI2jsdAmEK9zH82w</a><br />\n在统计的31块B365主板内，增强的有14块，不变的10块，缩水的有7块。在传统的四大板厂（华硕、技嘉、微星、华擎）的25块主板，只有4块缩水，增强的11块，不变的10块。已经可以证明B365系列主板并不是全部缩水，20%左右是缩水，45%左右增强，35%左右不变。缩水在贴牌系主板尤为严重差不多50%的缩水率。而价格上京东确实有定价比B360高100的，但京东实际到手价和淘宝价差距几乎都在50内，甚至有些B365卖的比B360便宜。"},{"pid":"f4f891ed3f6cb2bf346a6b5ea9d60941badac08e","tid":1679954,"uid":15808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb1427d36745c425f05caf67a11992230ef07d8c","tid":1679954,"uid":61763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:29:59.000Z","msg":"大陆仔就是硬核, 连登仔吃屎吧, 装逼仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av73494011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav73494011&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD51e0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=4bb6974f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av73494011</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/_aZGLeYI2jsdAmEK9zH82w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%